      "title": "The price of a liter of kerosene is up by Rs 253",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ceylon Petroleum Corporation has taken steps to raise the price of a liter of kerosene oil by 253 rupees from midnight today (21).",
        "The price of a liter of kerosene, which was 87 rupees, will become 340 rupees from midnight today."
      ],
